    "description": {
      "value": "<p>This Nindo is one of perseverance. The first time you are reduced to 0 Hit points by a hostile creature, you are instead reduced to 1 Hit point. You cannot go below this 1 hit point until the end of your next turn. When you fall unconscious or enter the dying condition, you roll your Death saving throws at advantage. You cannot gain the benefits of this feature more than once per rest.</p>",
